apropos.title: about us
apropos.paragraph1: COGEB International CGI is a limited liability company, entirely export-oriented and non-resident, established in 2002 in accordance with Law No. 94-42 of 07/03/1994, as amended and supplemented by Law No. 96-59 of 06/07/1996 and Law No. 98-102 of 30/11/1998.
apropos.paragraph2: With a capital of 250,000 dinars, COGEB International specializes in international trade, including the export and import of goods and products, as well as all types of international trading and brokerage operations.
